 Roland Roberts: Violín.
 Ian Rowbotham: Viola.
 Erica Simpson: Violonchelo.
 Metales, alive and kickin’ horns
 Noel Langley: Trompeta.
 Dennis Rollins: Trombón.
 Scott Garland: Saxo tenor.
 Otros:
 Marco Ricci: Coros.
 Ingrid Schroeder: Coros.
 Geoff Dunn: Batería.
 Geoff Hunt: Ingeniero sonido y mezclas.
 John Palmer: Ingeniero sonido.
 Yan Memnis: Asistente ingeniero.
Artista: Gary Moore
 LP: Still got the blues
 Año: 1990
 Productor: Gary Moore and Ian Taylor.
1. Moving on
2. Oh pretty woman
3. Walking by myself
4. Still got the blues
5. Texas strut
6. Too tired
7. King of the blues
8. As the years go passing by
9. Midnight blues
10. That kind of woman
11. All your love
12. Stop messin’ around
13. Bonustrack
Engineered and mixed by Ian Taylor with assistance from Steve Fitzmaurice, Noel Harris, Stuart Day, Marcus Draws, Greg Muden and Hayden Bendall.
String on “Still got the blues” and “Midnight blues” arranged by Gary Moore and
Don Airey. Strings conducted by Don Airey. All horns arranged by Gary Moore
and Don Airey.
All songs written by Gary Moore except:
2: Williams.
3: Jimmy Rodgers.
6: Johnny “Guitar” Watson/Maxwell Davies/Saul Bihari.
8: Dan Malone.
10: George Harrison.
11: Rush.
12: Peter Green.
