Artista: Gary Moore
 LP: After hours
 Año: 1992
 Productor: Gary Moore and Ian Taylor.
1. Cold Day in Hell
2. Don't You Lie to Me (I Get Evil)
3. Story of the Blues
4. Since I Met You Baby
5. Separate Ways
6. Only Fool in Town
7. Key to Love
8. Jumpin' at Shadows
9. The Blues Is Alright
10. The Hurt Inside
11. Nothing's the Same
Mixed by Ian Taylor except “Story of the blues” mixed by Gregg Jackman.
Engineered by Ian Taylor, Peter Hodgson and Hayden Bendall.
Assisted by Robin Barclay, Steve Fitzmaurice, Matt Lane, Ed Goldberg, Ellen Fitton,
Alec Firla and Andy Baker.
Brass & string arrangements by Gary Moore and Tommy Eyre. String section led by
Gavin Wright.
Special guests: B.B. King (4) and Albert Collins (9).
All songs written by Gary Moore except:
2: Hudson Whittaker
7: John Mayall
8: D. Bennett
9: Milton Campbell
Músicos:
 Keyboards: Tommy Eyre
